{"tid":810064,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2019DSE] 英文科／通識科免費改文 + Free Mock","createTime":"2018-09-07T15:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T03:12:50.000Z","uid":11058,"like":12,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4267d6b34890b458654eed7d31ce5722a586660d","tid":810064,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"2019年度 *連登限定* 免費改文又開始啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n19DSE既同學仔係時候溫書啦作文操卷啦<br />\n今次送多份免費Mock比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交文好簡單<br />\n免費！<br />\n唯一代價係比我用你交既文教書！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n作完文／做完通識卷<br />\n可以send去awenglishls@gmail.com<br />\n我會盡快幫你改+比comments<br />\n7-14日內send翻比你 <br />\n不論past papers定係出版社題目都可以架 <br />\n<br />\n你可以<br />\n1. send .doc比我<br />\n2. send SCAN既手寫文比我 (可以用手機dl camscanner)<br />\n(影相就唔改啦好難睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有問題都可以係到問！！<br />\n<br />\nMock卷可以係下面download<br />\n非巴絲就去我IG去拎啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/sh/jyn706e5ol4vbfj/AADYNvpdIh3Nj5gCMKiNJQcga?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fsh%2Fjyn706e5ol4vbfj%2FAADYNvpdIh3Nj5gCMKiNJQcga%3Fdl%3D0&d=LACzl6Du%2FRWIbUjHR75B0zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9b6182e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/sh/jyn706e5ol4vbfj/AADYNvpdIh3Nj5gCMKiNJQcga?dl=0</a><br />\n為左保障Mock卷唔會比有心人利用<br />\n做完之後麻煩大家IG Direct我拎答案啦~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：小組補習導師 主修英文 英文通識5** <br />\nig: awenglishls</span></span>"},{"pid":"bfb13b49584e987782cdf41a87fb6524d9c32122","tid":810064,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67db04f91fa056a3457d93a190d198e2e317e6f","tid":810064,"uid